OL,3,CTrain crash in Indonesia kills 14
OL,4,Cwomen and injures 84
OL,6,FA train crash in Indonesia has killed
OL,7,F14 people, all of whom were women,
OL,8,Fauthorities have said.
OL,10,FA long-distance train crashed into the
OL,11,Frear carriage of a stopped commuter
OL,12,Ftrain at Bekasi Timur Station, about
OL,13,F15 miles outside the capital, Jakarta,
OL,14,Flate on Monday evening.
OL,16,FThe carriage was designated for women
OL,17,Fonly, a common accommodation to stop
OL,18,Fharassment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
