OL,3,CTrain crash in Indonesia kills 14
OL,4,Cwomen and injures 84
OL,6,FRail officials say 84 injured people
OL,7,Fhave been taken to hospitals, with
OL,8,Frescuers recovering the last victims
OL,9,Fon Tuesday morning.
OL,11,FThe bodies of the dead were taken to a
OL,12,Fhospital for further identification.
OL,14,F"There are no further casualties,"
OL,15,Fsaid Mohammad Syafii, the head of the
OL,16,FNational Search and Rescue Agency.
OL,18,FAll of the 240 passengers on the Argo
OL,19,FBromo Anggrek long-distance train were
OL,20,Fsafe, officials said.
