OL,3,CTrain crash in Indonesia kills 14
OL,4,Cwomen and injures 84
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPolice are now investigating the cause
OL,12,Fof the incident, Jakarta Police Chief
OL,13,FAsep Edi Suheri told reporters at the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FAuthorities believe the incident began
OL,17,Fwhen another commuter train hit a
OL,18,Fstalled taxi near Bekasi Timur
OL,19,FStation, the Indonesian Ministry of
OL,20,FTransportation said in a statement.
