OL,3,CTrain crash in Indonesia kills 14
OL,4,Cwomen and injures 84
OL,6,FThis led staff to stop a second
OL,7,Fcommuter train at the station, where
OL,8,Fit was struck by the long-distance
OL,9,Ftrain.
OL,11,F"We are leaving it to the National
OL,12,FTransportation Safety Committee to
OL,13,Finvestigate the cause of tonight's
OL,14,Ftrain accident in greater detail,"
OL,15,Fsaid Bobby Rasyidin, CEO of state-
OL,16,Fowned railway company PT Kereta Api
OL,17,FIndonesia.
